### FASE 4 — INVENTORY / WAREHOUSE
### ============================================================

### 4.1 Crear bodega principal
### → Guardar warehouse_id en @warehouseId
POST {{baseUrl}}/warehouse
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branch_id": "{{branchId}}",
  "warehouse_name": "Bodega Central",
  "warehouse_address": "San José, La Uruca, Costa Rica"
}

###

### 4.2 Crear segunda bodega (para transferencias IN-01)
### → Guardar warehouse_id en @warehouseId2
POST {{baseUrl}}/warehouse
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "branch_id": "{{branchId2}}",
  "warehouse_name": "Bodega Norte",
  "warehouse_address": "Heredia, Costa Rica"
}

###

### 4.3 Agregar stock producto 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/product
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "warehouse_id": "{{warehouseId}}",
  "product_id": "{{variantId}}",
  "amount": 200,
  "expiration_date": "2026-12-31"
}

###

### 4.4 Agregar stock producto 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/product
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "warehouse_id": "{{warehouseId}}",
  "product_id": "{{variantId2}}",
  "amount": 500,
  "expiration_date": "2025-06-30"
}

###

### 4.5 Agregar stock producto 3 (con fecha próxima a vencer - para IN-04)
POST {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/product
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "warehouse_id": "{{warehouseId}}",
  "product_id": "{{variantId3}}",
  "amount": 50,
  "expiration_date": "2026-03-20"
}

###

### 4.6 Contar inventario de bodega
POST {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/count
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "warehouse_id": "{{warehouseId}}"
}

###

### 4.7 Consultar bodegas del tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/tenant/

###

### ─── IN-03: Consultar stock consolidado por warehouse ─────
### Sprint Backlog: Endpoint GET /warehouse/:warehouse_id/stock
GET {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/{{warehouseId}}/stock

###

### ─── IN-01: Transferir inventario entre bodegas ───────────
### Sprint Backlog: Transacción atómica + actualización de stock
### → Guardar transfer_id en @transferId
POST {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "origin_warehouse_id": "{{warehouseId}}",
  "destination_warehouse_id": "{{warehouseId2}}",
  "tenant_id": "{{tenantId}}",
  "products": [
    {
      "product_id": "{{variantId}}",
      "amount": 50
    },
    {
      "product_id": "{{variantId2}}",
      "amount": 100
    }
  ]
}

###

### 4.8 Verificar stock después de transferencia (origen)
GET {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/{{warehouseId}}/stock

###

### 4.9 Verificar stock después de transferencia (destino)
GET {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/{{warehouseId2}}/stock

###

### 4.10 Crear reporte de discrepancia
### → Guardar discrepancy_count_id en @discrepancyId
POST {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/discrepancy-report
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": "{{variantId}}",
  "warehouse_id": "{{warehouseId}}",
  "stored_quantity": 150,
  "physical_quantity": 145,
  "discrepancy_reason": "Producto dañado durante almacenamiento - 5 unidades"
}

###

### 4.11 Ver reportes de discrepancia
GET {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/discrepancy-report/{{warehouseId}}

###

### ─── IN-02: Aplicar ajuste por discrepancia ───────────────
### Sprint Backlog: PATCH /warehouse/discrepancy-report/:id/apply
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/discrepancy-report/{{discrepancyId}}/apply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenant_id": "{{tenantId}}"
}

###

### ─── IN-04: Consultar productos próximos a vencer ─────────
### Sprint Backlog: GET /warehouse/expiring?days=30
GET {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/expiring?days=30

###

### 4.12 Consultar log de movimientos de inventario
GET {{baseUrl}}/warehouse/{{warehouseId}}/log

###


