### FASE 5 — PURCHASE (COMPRAS / PROVEEDORES)
### ============================================================

### 5.1 Crear proveedor
### → Guardar supplier_id en @supplierId
POST {{baseUrl}}/suppliers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplier_name": "Papelería Nacional S.A.",
  "supplier_contact_info": "ventas@papnacional.cr | +506 2222-3333",
  "supplier_address": "Barrio Amón, San José, Costa Rica",
  "supplier_notes": "Proveedor preferido para artículos de oficina"
}

###

### 5.2 Consultar proveedores
GET {{baseUrl}}/suppliers

###

### 5.3 Crear orden de compra
### → Guardar purchase_order_id en @purchaseOrderId
### → Guardar purchase_account_payable_id en @accountPayableId
POST {{baseUrl}}/purchase
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplier_id": "{{supplierId}}",
  "warehouse_id": "{{warehouseId}}",
  "expected_delivery_date": "2026-04-15",
  "has_invoice": true,
  "payment_condition": "30",
  "items": [
    {
      "product_variant_id": "{{variantId}}",
      "quantity_ordered": 100,
      "unit_price": 1200
    },
    {
      "product_variant_id": "{{variantId2}}",
      "quantity_ordered": 200,
      "unit_price": 250
    }
  ]
}

###

### ─── CO-01: Consultar todas las órdenes de compra ─────────
### Sprint Backlog: GET /purchase
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchase

###

### ─── CO-01: Consultar orden de compra por ID ──────────────
### Sprint Backlog: GET /purchase/:id
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchase/{{purchaseOrderId}}

###

### ─── CO-03: Transición de estado: Pending → Shipped ───────
### Sprint Backlog: PATCH /purchase/:id/status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/purchase/{{purchaseOrderId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status_id": 2,
  "tenant_id": "{{tenantId}}"
}

###

### ─── CO-03: Transición de estado: Shipped → Delivered ─────
### Sprint Backlog: Activa trigger create_goods_receipt + three-way matching
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/purchase/{{purchaseOrderId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status_id": 3,
  "tenant_id": "{{tenantId}}"
}

###

### ─── CO-04: Consultar three-way matching ──────────────────
### Sprint Backlog: GET /purchase/:id/matching
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchase/{{purchaseOrderId}}/matching

###

### ─── CO-02: Registrar pago parcial de orden ───────────────
### Sprint Backlog: POST /purchase/payment
### → Guardar payment_id en @purchasePaymentId
POST {{baseUrl}}/purchase/payment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purchase_account_payable_id": "{{accountPayableId}}",
  "amount_paid": 100000,
  "payment_method_id": 2,
  "payment_reference": "TRANSF-001-2026",
  "payment_date": "2026-03-10"
}

###

### 5.4 Consultar estado de cuenta por pagar
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchase/{{purchaseOrderId}}/account-payable

###

### ─── CO-02: Registrar pago final (completa la cuenta) ─────
POST {{baseUrl}}/purchase/payment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purchase_account_payable_id": "{{accountPayableId}}",
  "amount_paid": 70000,
  "payment_method_id": 3,
  "payment_reference": "TC-VISA-2026",
  "payment_date": "2026-03-15"
}

###

